@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_efbdog(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = ((wp.sin(tmp + 0.37) * wp.sin(v1 + 0.52)) + 0.33)
    tmp = 0.02
    v1 = v1
    v1 = wp.cos(wp.abs((v1 + 0.96 + v0 + 0.04)))
    tmp = (wp.exp(v1) / wp.exp(wp.sin(v2 + 0.21)))
    v0 = (0.63 * wp.exp(wp.sin(v2 + 0.90)))
    tmp = wp.cos((wp.exp(v2 + 0.99) - tmp))
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.cos(v1))
    data[tid] = v0
